      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div
            class="w-4 h-4 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/30"
          >
          </div>
          <span>Core Expertise - Daily use</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div
            class="w-4 h-4 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full border-2 border-emerald-300"
          >
          </div>
          <span>Regular - Production experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div
            class="w-4 h-4 bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-emerald-200"
          >
          </div>
          <span>Exploring - Learning & experimenting</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-4 italic">
        ðŸ’¡ Hover over any skill to see years of experience
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div
        class="bg-linear-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-2">10+</div>
